    "However, there exist certain limitations to achieving the same level of efficacy in medical and bioinformatics applications.",
    "In general, research in this area is still ongoing.",
    "One of the most salient issues is the scarcity of large datasets containing high-quality patterns for training purposes.",
    "In such cases, data integration may be viable for amalgamating information from multiple sources.",
